	Relax with Sai Om&rsquo;s lavender incense while it fills the air with floral fragrances. Lavender is famed for its relaxing properties and is one of the most easily recognised aromas.&nbsp;This lovely aroma has a balancing effect on the mind and body, soothing your cares away and creating a refuge away from the stresses of modern life. To use simply place an incense stick into an incense holder or burner and light the tip. Once the&nbsp;tip is glowing, carefully blow out the flame and enjoy the wonderful aromas that fill the room. Choose between one box which contains 15g of incense (approximately 14 sticks) or a value pack of 12 boxes (approximately 154 sticks).</p>
